    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "This 2002 Porsche 911 Carrera (996.2) features the refined 3.6L flat-six Boxer engine with VarioCam Plus, delivering a linear torque curve and 320 hp. The G96 6-speed manual gearbox offers precise gate engagement, paired with a chassis that remains taut thanks to well-maintained MacPherson front struts and a multi-link rear setup. Critically, the IMS bearing has been addressed with a dual-row ceramic upgrade, and the rear main seal (RMS) shows no signs of weeping. The naturally aspirated induction provides immediate throttle response, while the ventilated four-piston Monobloc calipers provide consistent thermal management under load. A mechanically sorted driver\u2019s car for the purist.",
